				p Through an artificial inteligence algorithm able to find patterns in the user behavior, we measure basic feelings like trust, fear, interest or hesitation for each session.
				
			.results
				img(width="220px" src="img/results.svg")
				h2 We deliver smart information
				p What about start a mailing campaign with hesitant users, or customize your website according to the visitor's feelings? We provide the output you need to potentiate your sales!.
		
		.subscribe-section
			.filter
			.content
				h3 Want to be part of next generation analytics?
				button.button.full.purple.lg Request your free invitation now!
				button.button.outline.purple.lg Know more about us
				
